    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has notable mechanical issues that will require attention before reliable daily use. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible damage and cosmetic deterioration. The interior is worn with stains, tears, or other damage. Best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts vehicle.",
